MultilabelChainEnsemble - Class in rdt.model
Class to represent an ensemble of MultilabelChainTrees.
MultilabelChainEnsemble(CollectorPreferences, int, int, int, long, double, double, int, MultilabelChainEnsemble.PredictType, MultilabelChainEnsemble.ChainType) - Constructor for class rdt.model.MultilabelChainEnsemble
Creates a new MultilabelChainEnsemble with the given information about the learning tasks, the number of trees, the maximal depth of the trees, the minimum number of instances to create a splitter, a seed for the random number generator, the percentage of label-splitters in the ensemble, the percentage of the label-splitters which are activated, the number of how many labels should be predicted with the chain method, the type of prediction and the type how to predict the next label.
MultilabelChainEnsemble.ChainType - Enum in rdt.model
The type how the the next label is chosen.
MultilabelChainEnsemble.PredictType - Enum in rdt.model
The type of prediction, which is used.
